export const STUDENT = [
  {
    left: {
      id: "firstName",
      name: "firstName",
      label: "First Name",
      className: "select-button-2",
      type: "text",
      disabled: false,
      show: true,
    },
    right: {
      id: "lastName",
      name: "lastName",
      label: "Last Name",
      className: "select-button-2",
      type: "text",
      disabled: false,
      show: true,
    }
  },
  {
    id: "email",
    name: "email",
    label: "Email",
    className: "select-button-2",
    type: "email",
    disabled: false,
    show: true,
    side: "left",
  },
  {
    id: "courseOfStudy",
    name: "courseOfStudy",
    label: "Course Of Study",
    className: "select-button-2",
    type: "text",
    disabled: false,
    show: true,
    side: "left",
  },
  {
    id: "faculty",
    name: "faculty",
    label: "Faculty",
    className: "select-button-2",
    type: "text",
    disabled: false,
    show: true,
    side: "left",
  },
  ,
  {
    id: "contactNo",
    name: "contactNo",
    label: "Contact No",
    className: "select-button-2",
    type: "number",
    disabled: false,
    show: true,
    side: "right",
  },
  {
    id: "academicYear",
    name: "academicYear",
    label: "Academic Year",
    className: "select-button-2",
    type: "text",
    disabled: false,
    show: true,
    side: "right",
  },
  {
    id: "department",
    name: "department",
    label: "Department",
    className: "select-button-2",
    type: "text",
    disabled: false,
    show: true,
    side: "right",
  },
];
